      <title>中国对汽车袭击事件悼念者进行噤声，誓言加强社会管控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/china-silences-car-attack-mourners-vows-tighter-grip-on-society</link>
      <description><![CDATA[到周三下午，中国多年来已知的最致命平民暴力事件的发生地笼罩在一种诡异的寂静中。当车辆畅通无阻地驶过现已空无一人的珠海体育中心体育场时，一名身着黄黑相间衣服的美团快递员骑着摩托车停了下来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/china-silences-car-attack-mourners-vows-tighter-grip-on-society</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 04:30:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的政府效率部门到底能做什么？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/doge-what-can-musk-do-with-the-department-of-government-efficiency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普希望废除联邦官僚机构，甚至取消至少一个联邦部门。为此，他正在创建一个名为政府效率部的新机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/doge-what-can-musk-do-with-the-department-of-government-efficiency</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 03:44:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦卡锡称参议院将阻止特朗普对盖茨的提名</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/trump-pick-of-matt-gaetz-will-be-rejected-by-senate-mccarthy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前众议院议长凯文·麦卡锡预测，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普提名马特·盖茨出任司法部长的提议明年将被共和党参议院否决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/trump-pick-of-matt-gaetz-will-be-rejected-by-senate-mccarthy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 02:14:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡领导人寻求通过议会投票增强权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/sri-lanka-leader-seeks-to-bolster-power-with-parliamentary-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡举行了该党外来左翼总统获胜以来的首次议会选举，以检验其打击腐败和修改不受欢迎的国际货币基金组织贷款计划的雄心勃勃的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/sri-lanka-leader-seeks-to-bolster-power-with-parliamentary-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的非常规选择都具有一个关键品质：忠诚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/trump-picks-for-top-jobs-stress-loyalty-culture-wars-tv-skills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普决定提名极端忠诚的马特·盖茨担任司法部长，此举震惊了华盛顿。这一举动进一步证实了自他开始宣布提名以来就显而易见的事实：对特朗普的服从是获得这份工作的主要条件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/trump-picks-for-top-jobs-stress-loyalty-culture-wars-tv-skills</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 23:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦考密克和凯西将为宾夕法尼亚州参议员竞选重新计票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/mccormick-and-casey-head-to-recount-in-pennsylvania-senate-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宾夕法尼亚州联邦秘书阿尔施密特周三晚间宣布，宾夕法尼亚州美国参议院席位竞选的非正式结果已引发全州范围内依法重新计票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/mccormick-and-casey-head-to-recount-in-pennsylvania-senate-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 22:55:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Polymarket 因涉嫌允许美国用户在平台上投注而受到美国司法部调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/polymarket-investigated-by-doj-for-letting-us-users-bet-on-platform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国司法部正在调查加密预测投注平台 Polymarket 涉嫌接受来自美国用户的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/polymarket-investigated-by-doj-for-letting-us-users-bet-on-platform</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 22:52:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普盟友盖茨被任命为司法部长，辞去众议院席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/trump-taps-loyalist-lawmaker-matt-gaetz-for-attorney-general</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普提名众议员马特·盖茨担任司法部长，任命一位两极分化、陷入困境的议员重塑美国执法部门，并执行其在移民、犯罪和热点社会问题上的议程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/trump-taps-loyalist-lawmaker-matt-gaetz-for-attorney-general</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 20:33:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普赢得共和党三连胜，共和党保留众议院多数席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/republicans-keep-control-of-us-house-in-power-sweep</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党在美国众议院保持微弱多数，使得唐纳德·特朗普及其政党统一控制民选政府部门，并限制了对新任总统权力的潜在限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/republicans-keep-control-of-us-house-in-power-sweep</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 19:20:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登与习近平举行会晤，世界领导人将焦点转向特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/biden-xi-to-meet-at-apec-as-world-leaders-shift-focus-to-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国政府高级官员透露，美国总统乔·拜登将于周六在秘鲁会见中国国家主席习近平，这是美国总统任期内两国领导人最后一次面对面会谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/biden-xi-to-meet-at-apec-as-world-leaders-shift-focus-to-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 17:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
